Privacy Policy

Effective Date: June 18, 2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to Fishy, your shield against phishing and scam messages. Your privacy is important to us, and this Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app.

2. Information We Collect

No Personal Information Collected: Fishy does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users. We do not require you to provide any personal details to use our app.

Usage Data: We may collect non-personal information about how you use our app, including the screens you visit, the features you use, and the time you spend on the app. This information is collected to improve the functionality and user experience of our app.

Device Information: We may collect non-personal information about the device you use to access our app, such as the device model, operating system, and unique device identifiers. This information is used solely for the purpose of enhancing our app’s compatibility and performance.

Uploaded Images: The images you upload to the app are used solely to analyze and determine if they contain phishing or scam messages. The text extracted from these images is sent to our analysis service and is not stored or shared.

3. How We Use Your Information

Since we do not collect personal information, we use the non-personal information we collect for the following purposes:

To Provide and Improve Our Services: We use usage data and device information to operate, maintain, and enhance the app’s functionality.
To Analyze Usage: We use usage data to understand how users interact with our app and to make improvements.
To Analyze Uploaded Images: We use the text extracted from the images you upload to determine if they contain phishing or scam messages.
4. Information Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your information to outside parties. Since we do not collect personal information, there is no personal information to share or disclose.

5. Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the non-personal information we collect from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no internet or email transmission is ever fully secure or error-free. Please keep this in mind when using our app.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at fishyapp@protonmail.com.
